transcript_text: Sundar Pichai just knocked out Sam Altman in one single day. We've announced over a dozen models and research breakthroughs. He released these 13 crazy AI updates in Google I.O. Number 10 will blow your mind. You can see the change here. Let's get into this. One. Try on AI for shopping. You upload your photo. Google shows how clothes will look on your body. Folds, shape, everything. Like it? Click once, it buys it for you. Two. New AI search tab. Google now has a special AI tab. You can ask longer questions, follow up like a chat, and it remembers your topic. Three. Search that takes action. Looking for a ticket or restaurant. Google doesn't just give links. It finds the best one and books it for you. Four. Chrome just got smart. While you browse any page, Gemini AI is there. It explains, compares, and answers without switching tabs. Five. Gemini as your assistant. Looking for a flat? Gemini finds listings, filters them, and even books tours for you. Six. AI agents that work together. Google made it possible for different AI tools to talk to each other, even from other companies. Your AI can now team up. Seven. Project Mariner. This AI can use the internet like a human. It clicks, scrolls, fills forms, and learns what to do after seeing it just once. Eight. Jules. AI for coding. You tell it what to build. It writes code, fixes bugs, updates files, and explains every step. Ninth. Imagine 4. Image maker. Type anything. It creates beautiful, realistic pictures. Better hands, better light, even perfect text on posters. Ten. Flow. AI for filmmakers. Describe a scene. It gives you camera shots, angles, characters. Turn text into movies. Add music with Lyria. Eleventh. Lyria. AI for music. Need music? Lyria makes full songs with vocals, melody, even choirs. Real artists are already using it. Twelve. XR glasses with AI. These smart glasses translate languages, guide you, and even remember what you saw earlier. Like having Google in your eyes. Thirteen. Google Ultra plan. Want early access to all of this? The Ultra plan gives it to you. Plus, more power, more tools, and YouTube Premium included. This isn't coming soon. It's already here. Which update blew your mind? Comment, save this, and follow. Because this is just the beginning.
